rows.label: tlk42100152_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Ugh, how awful! This
country is too hot.

rows.label: tlk42100152_03_msg0002
rows.name:
In this heat, won't the
Divine Beast get exhausted
and fall into the Cloud Sea?

rows.label: tlk42100152_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Since humans did this to the
Divine Beast, I wish humans
would do something about it.

rows.label: tlk42100152_03_msg0004
rows.name:
If it does fall, I'll sneak onto
a ship and go to Liberalitas.

rows.label: tlk42100152_03_msg0005
rows.name:
I heard the Demon King is
gone, so I want to try
visiting the Phonex colony!
